{"id":"xpoinittest-ad5f64","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-317e0aeb-930b-4694-ae58-1d731ac046e9","text":"## Summary\n\n- Added `clearLines()` to `src/game/board.ts` — filters out full rows, prepends empty rows, returns lines cleared count\n- Updated `lock()` and `hardDrop()` in `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — call `clearLines` after `lockPiece`\n\n## Rationale\n\nLine clearing is a pure board transformation — filter full rows, count them, pad top. Placed in `board.ts` alongside `createBoard`. Both lock paths (gravity + hard drop) now clear lines.\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. 1–4 line clears working. Ready for review."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:35:28.861403Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
