{"id":"xpoinittest-3bc263","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Add L and J tetromino pieces","description":"## What\n\nAdd the L-piece and J-piece (mirrored L) tetrominoes to the game, bringing the piece count to 6.\n\n## Pieces\n\n- **L:** 3x1 bar with a 1x1 block on the right end of the bottom row\n- **J:** 3x1 bar with a 1x1 block on the left end of the bottom row (mirror of L)\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] L-piece defined with all 4 rotation states and a distinct color\n- [ ] J-piece defined with all 4 rotation states and a distinct color\n- [ ] Both pieces appear in random piece selection\n- [ ] Rotation and wall kicks work correctly for both pieces","status":"BACKLOG","parent_id":"xpoinittest-69a413","estimate":1,"sort_order":"a8","dependencies":[{"source_id":"xpoinittest-3bc263","target_id":"xpoinittest-5432c1","kind":"depends_on"}],"labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:38:44.239667Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
