{"id":"xpoinittest-5a8e82","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Add S tetromino piece","description":"## What\n\nAdd the S-piece (mirror of Z) to the game, bringing the piece count to 7 — the full classic COLORBLOXX set.\n\n## Piece\n\n- **S:** Two 2x1 rows offset by one column, mirrored from Z\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] S-piece defined with all 4 rotation states and a distinct color (green)\n- [ ] S-piece appears in random piece selection\n- [ ] Rotation and wall kicks work correctly","status":"PLANNED","parent_id":"xpoinittest-69a413","estimate":1,"sort_order":"a0","dependencies":[{"source_id":"xpoinittest-5a8e82","target_id":"xpoinittest-5432c1","kind":"depends_on"}],"labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:40:35.852985Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
