{"id":"xpoinittest-3bc263","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-c1437d08-7ffa-4a6e-8d86-be09c1524277","text":"## Summary\n\nAdded L (orange `#f0a000`) and J (blue `#0000f0`) tetrominoes to `src/game/pieces.ts` with all 4 rotation states each. Added both to `TETROMINOES` array.\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Both pieces appear in game. Ready for review."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:41:01.248261Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
{"id":"xpoinittest-5a8e82","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-595934a5-7544-4ab0-a9f1-b57ca333b288","text":"## Summary\n\nAdded S-piece (green `#00f000`) to `src/game/pieces.ts` with all 4 rotation states. Added to `TETROMINOES` array, completing the classic 7-piece COLORBLOXX set.\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. S-piece appears in game. Ready for review."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:41:02.102531Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
